data.description: Paid solar! Horse property with irrigation. Beautifully upgraded main residence with an open floor plan with updated features, new flooring with custom trim, completely redone wood fireplace surround and extra space added with a comfy built-in loft. Space for toys in the two attached two car garages. Relax in the master bedroom and your fully remodeled master bathroom with soaking garden tub. Two room guest house w/garage. Entertain effortlessly under covered patio & pool overlooking 2.2 acres!
